{"tid":2040081,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"爆料者100%肯定Sony6月公佈38款PS5遊戲","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T15:10:40.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ea2f5f0d35706ba4b01e500a9a6949add8baff","tid":2040081,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"爆料者100%肯定Sony6月公佈38款PS5遊戲<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202005/26/17c6ad03de67679f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202005%2F26%2F17c6ad03de67679f.jpg&h=af120ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據Kaan Can Oyman透漏的OPM（Official Playstation Magazine）官方雜誌內容，Sony將於6月展示38款PS5遊戲，但目前沒有得到官方正式報導。另外知名媒體人Tom Warren也轉發了這條雜誌內容並表示「不要對這38款遊戲感到太激動，除非你對XSX的遊戲也感到激動」，另外據雜誌封面，這38款遊戲已經確認登錄PS5並且將公佈演示。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202005/26/43cccdea03d50d36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202005%2F26%2F43cccdea03d50d36.png&h=4a1e69b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202005/26/14adb572454aef5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202005%2F26%2F14adb572454aef5e.jpg&h=fe37ed7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202005/26/9916ae38a2be6020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202005%2F26%2F9916ae38a2be6020.jpg&h=423994e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4430e7bbc1a5a66f22516be4481aaa7a0414098b","tid":2040081,"uid":4857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"WARFRAME都要TBC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a664106a3da754bd9e58b6d57cca31814bc899","tid":2040081,"uid":356254,"l